review.description: Nice people, in season vegetables picked daily. I made dill pickles and mixed vegetable pickles with their produce, both batches turned out nice and crisp.
review.author: Nelly K.

review.description:
A convenient little stop to pick up produce off of Highway 45 in Antioch. They don't have a huge selection, but we found some good things. They also carry honey and home made jams and jellies.

BTW, best nectarines I have ever had! Extremely sweet and juicy!
review.author: Pam D.
